Knife Fight - Season 3, Episode 7


Round 1: Python

New Jersey farm-to-table chef, David Felton, takes on Leah Cohen and her Asian influenced cuisine. Tonight they'll need to get the votes of our judges, Naomi Pomeroy and Kris Morningstar, and serve up one killer ingredient.




Knife Fight - Season 3, Episode 8


Round 1: Eels

Boston chef Tony Maws takes on New York colleague Vincent Chirico; selected ingredients include live eel, bone marrow and matsutake. The chefs do their best to impress judges Naomi Pomeroy and Kris Morningstar and make it to the next round.




Original Air Date: 16-Jun-2015
